defaultUK
default typically would be formed under the UK Companies Act.
default 
defaultThat is a piece of legislation that deals with 
defaulta
default company’s constitution and how it operates.
default L
defaultisting is a generic term; we might get on to talking about some of the 
defaultnuances of what it means a bit later
default, but e
defaultssentially it is 
defaultabout
default access to capital markets.
default 
